msItem.note:
The list originally contained nine items, covering ff. 138r-155v; a further
                                    eleven items were later added, covering ff. 156r-168r, probably by the same hand;
                                    another hand added two more items, covering ff. 168v-176v

Similar to Notitia 10 (ed. Darrouzès); the latter part differs
                                    from the text in the edition: the text after line 729 is absent,
                                    and instead the bishoprics subordinate to Kiev are listed
